@startuml
title Diagrama de Secuencia - Crear Aula

actor "Administrador" as Admin
participant "Frontend (React)" as FE
participant "API (FastAPI)" as API
participant "AulaService" as Service
participant "AulaRepository" as Repo
database "Base de Datos" as DB

Admin -> FE: Clic en "Nueva Aula"
activate FE
FE --> Admin: Mostrar Formulario
Admin -> FE: Ingresa datos (Nombre, Capacidad, Edificio) y Guardar
FE -> API: POST /aulas (AulaCreate JSON)
activate API
API -> Service: crear_aula(aula_create)
activate Service
Service -> Repo: create(aula_model)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB: INSERT INTO aulas ...
activate DB
DB --> Repo: ID nueva aula
deactivate DB
Repo --> Service: Aula (con ID)
deactivate Repo
Service --> API: AulaResponse
deactivate Service
API --> FE: 201 Created (Aula JSON)
deactivate API
FE -> FE: Actualizar Lista / Notificar Éxito
FE --> Admin: Mostrar "Aula creada correctamente"
deactivate FE

@enduml
